Combine rice noodles, peanuts, vegetables, powdered peanut butter, chicken bouillon, cilantro, chia seeds, salt, garlic powder, ginger, garlic powder, black pepper, and cayenne pepper in a resealable plastic bag. Remove air and seal. Reconstitute rice noodle mixture by pouring in 1 cup boiling water. Mix well and let cook until noodles and vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.